snippet.title: Rocky - Sega Master System Full Game
snippet.description: Speed Run of Rocky for the Sega Master System using turbo controller. I needed the turbo controls to get really high results in the training rounds. If you over-achieve in training rounds you get stronger and faster punches. Ex. Watch the round against Drago where power punches can be thrown in 3 punch combos instead  4.
